name: The mountain I went to meet
description:
My travels have been always to go after and looking for how I feel in some places. My obsession with the mountains many times guided me.

That day I reach very high in the Himalayas. The sunrise started when we were up there and I felt grateful and exhausted, after trekking for four days to reach that moment. 
I was in Nepal and the mountain remain inside of me. When I have to take myself to a peaceful place, I think of them.

Mountains are respect and humility in the purest form.
I will keep this moment till my end.

Picture from MARDI HIMAL TREK - ANNAPURNA - HIMALAYAS - NEPAL
Created in 2019
